name: Female Sexual Liberation
description:
Women are wonderful! With all their (sexual) needs, peculiarities and desires. Unfortunately not everyone saw and still does not see it that way. The history of femininity and especially of female sexuality is full of compulsions, prohibitions and misunderstandings. And it is marked by a struggle for equality and self-determination. 
It’s time to change this and liberate our desires!

For personal non-commercial use. Find us on Instagram and Twitter: @kinkykarrot
